# 1 - Data Understanding & Exploratory Data Analysis

## Objective

Understand the Housing dataset and identify important patterns before any preprocessing or modeling.

---

## Topics Covered

- Dataset overview
- Numerical & categorical features
- Missing value analysis
- Target variable analysis
- Distribution analysis
- Correlation analysis
- Rare category analysis

---

## Key Findings

- SalePrice is positively skewed with higher end outliers.

- OverallQual and Living Area has the strongest correlations with SalePrice.

- Categorical Features like Street and Utilites have rare categories which can be clubbed

- Multiple numerical variables contain extreme outliers.

- Expensive thing like Pool(PoolQc) is Missing in Almost all houses

